```html
<!doctype html>
<input id="s" type="number" value="10">
<button onclick="go()">Start</button>
<span id="t"></span>
<script>
function go() {
  let n = +s.value;
  t.textContent = n;
  let id = setInterval(() => {
    if (--n <= 0) { clearInterval(id); t.textContent = 0; alert("Done!"); }
    else t.textContent = n;
  }, 1000);
}
</script>
```

